  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK535">
<l>muṉṉuṟak kāvā tiḻukkiyāṉ ṟaṉpiḻai </l>
<l> piṉṉū ṟiraṅki viṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The thoughtless man, who provides not against the calamities that may happen, will afterwards repent for his fault.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
